</div> <!--Initiative page content condensed-->
<section class="supergirl">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1">
            <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Images/SuperGirl.jpg" alt="Girl in Cape from Global Goals Getty Images" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="pagelist">
                <div class="banner"><h1>What is EQUITY?</h1></div>

                <ul>
                    <li><h4>Provocative platform to end gender, racial and religious stereotypes that feed global inequity</h4></li>
                    <li><h4>2017 Focus is GENDER EQUITY, recognizing the intersectionality across race and religion</h4></li>
                    <li><h4>Event takes place Sept 21, 2017 – International Day of Peace</h4></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div> <!--row-->
</section> <!-- Supergirl -->
<section class="partners">
    <div>
        <h2 class="sectionTilte">
            Who is supporting EQUITY?
        </h2>
        <h3>
            In collaboration with the UN's Sustainable Development Goals, In Compact, and Global Citizen
            Partnering with leading global corporations and NGOs
        </h3>
        <div class="row">
            <img class="img-responsive col-sm-9" src="~/Images/UNLogoSDG.png" alt="The UN Sustainable Goals Logo" />
            <img class="img-responsive col-sm-3" src="~/Images/GlobalCitizenLogo.png" alt="The Global Citizen Logo" />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="TheHow">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6 col-sm-offset-1">
            <img src="~/Images/GenderEqPlus.png" width="100%" alt="Gender Equity Symbol from Global Goals" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="sectionTilte"><br />How will EQUITY be launched?<br /><br /><br /></div>
            <ul>
                <li><h4>Using an emotive storyline across VR, AR, visual arts, poetry, music, comedy, and dance</h4></li>
                <li><h4>The Digital Accountability Mosaic Network (D.A.M.N.) will be the centerpiece of the story</h4></li>
                <li><h4>Launched as an artistic digital interactive installation online, and within the EQUITY app, powered by AI</h4></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="EquityGoal">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2">
            <div><img src="~/Images/GlobalGoalsColorWheel.jpg" width="100%" alt="The Global Goals Color Wheel" /></div>
            <div><img src="~/Images/Woman in Car.jpg" width="100%" alt="Global Goals woman In Car from Getty Images" /></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <div class="sectionTilte"><br /><br />What is EQUITY's goal?<br /><br /></div>
            <ul>
                <li><h4>To ignite measurable actions towards achieving GENDER EQUITY in the path to achieve the GLOBAL GOALS by 2030</h4></li>
                <li><h4>Event planned for March 2018 during Global Goals week & UN General Assembly</h4></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div> <!--row-->
</section>

